# Python 3.12 PEG Grammar — Rule Names
# Extracted from https://github.com/python/cpython/blob/v3.12.0/Grammar/python.gram
# Excludes invalid_* rules (error recovery only).
#
# This file is the canonical list of grammar rules that Clython must implement.
# The unit test in tests/unit/test-grammar-coverage.lisp verifies every rule
# listed here has a corresponding implementation in the parser.

# Starting rules
file
interactive
eval
func_type
fstring

